Extrahepatic morbidities and mortality of NAFLD: an umbrella review of meta-analyses.
Patients with NAFLD are at heightened risk of extrahepatic outcomes. However, the certainty of evidence is only from very low to moderate. Further studies at low risk of bias are required to support the evidence and elucidate any causal associations.
